        "receiver": "{{receiver}}",
        "delay": 60000, 
        "message": {
            "text": "i'm fine, thank you!"
        }
    },
]

request.description:
Send message to multiple person.

You can also set custom `delay` between each message by adding the delay (in milliseconds) to the `delay` properties. Default value is `1000` if you don't provide any delay or you provide an invalid delay.

Example:

``` javascript
[
  {
    "receiver": "628231xxxxx",
    // 1000ms / 1 seconds delay before it try to send the message since we don't provide any delay
    "message": {
      "text": "hi! how are you?"
    }
  },
  {
    "receiver": "628950xxxxx",
    "delay": 60000, // 1 minutes delay before it try to send the message
    "message": {
      "text": "i'm fine, thank you!"
    }
  }
]

```

